Package se.kth.akok.index.geometries.point

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicPolygonPoint
    Basic polygon point is associated with a single polygon.
    BoundaryPoint
    BoundaryPoint is a point on the boundary, usually an evelope that contains the polygons in the scene.
    IncomingPoint
    Incoming point is a point on an edge of a polygon.
    PolygonPoint
    A polygon point has a set of visible, shadow and boundary rays.
    ShadowPoint
    A shadow point is the end point of the extended ray that starts from a polygon point A to a visible point B.
    VisiblePoint
    A visible point is a point that can be seen from a given polygon point.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ShadowPointType
    SAME_OBJECT shadow point on the extension of an adjacent edge.
    VisibleType
    SAME_OBJECT_VISIBLE A visible point that is on the same edge of a polygon.
